{"tid":2142031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1990年,黃崇厚先生於律政署出任助理檢察官","createTime":"2020-08-06T06:27:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T07:10:43.000Z","uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9933f10b74a178b35b8b6d39b1cd1f372c5f5ea9","tid":2142031,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:27:17.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">法官黃崇厚又係律政司的人<br />\n1995(現刑事檢控專員)梁卓然，任職檢察官<br />\n1990 黃崇厚考到助理檢察官<br />\n兩位人兄一定認識,律政編制唔大</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200009/06/0906174.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F200009%2F06%2F0906174.htm&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=98094205\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200009/06/0906174.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n委任司法人員<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n<br />\n下稿代司法機構發:<br />\n<br />\n司法機構今日（九月六日）宣布<strong>委任黃崇厚先生為裁判官</strong>，任期由二○○○年九月七日起生效。<br />\n<br />\n黃崇厚先生的簡歷如下：<br />\n<br />\n黃崇厚先生一九五七年在香港出生，一九八九年在英國伯明翰大學取得法學學位。一九九零年分別在香港和英國獲頒大律師資格<strong>。同年加入當時的律政署出任助理檢察官。先後於一九九一年及九四年晉升為檢察官和高級檢察官。</strong><br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n二○○○年九月六日（星期三）"},{"pid":"689005a63dd45bfa54a12112b2db275a885b38b1","tid":2142031,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:40:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd75971311b59b6aedf23dced6a1d906982f1943","tid":2142031,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1761288b9a6b617b571e6141baf65f0d887078b","tid":2142031,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"689005a63dd45bfa54a12112b2db275a885b38b1","tid":2142031,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:40:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:57:01.000Z","msg":"寫刑事檢控科xxx的係正式人員,特別去到檢察官得好少人,成日約埋食飯都似<br />\n<br />\n至於外判主控官係人手不足,或者<strong>屈9傷殘左的警暴受害人驚比人制裁</strong>判出去,其實唔認識就正常"},{"pid":"81d2d6da02fc56dcf1bc4f41421d15852f7f5bfb","tid":2142031,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T07:10:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}